{"tid":1842114,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"衰d講句  醫護唔罷 死既就係香港人","createTime":"2020-01-25T14:00:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T14:27:00.000Z","uid":246375,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5ae84b3b44b984c3b515df936329766a984fcd05","tid":1842114,"uid":246375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T14:00:08.000Z","msg":"我諗好多香港人都理解醫院要緊守崗位, 病人優先既心態<br />\n但前提係有個負責任既政府<br />\n<br />\n而家港共政府擺明想清洗香港人,係咁放大陸人落黎<br />\n而家已經有5宗確診,將來一定會越黎越多<br />\n只會有更多無辜既香港人中招<br />\n唔堵截源頭,做咩防護都無用<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻, 只有醫護罷工,係唯一一個可以令政府不得不封關既手段<br />\n你地肯罷,香港人一定支持同理解"},{"pid":"4d87ce9b538ebcc46c4373b4bc233bc2c00c3248","tid":1842114,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T14:03:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/itYniXi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FitYniXi.png&h=f849705a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港人死撚緊"},{"pid":"12d94759cbb4f7ce29ecfc76e25953d93dc964a0","tid":1842114,"uid":246375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T14:06:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"578ad9adc6dae0c2b6afdb360d5b24931aef3a3f","tid":1842114,"uid":246375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T14:09:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4f47709fc9aa8b48630cdcee66a8d537c09d6dfe","tid":1842114,"uid":246375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T14:27:00.000Z","msg":"推"}]}